{"type":"message","id":"a999e5e6","parentId":"bfc81d5a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:29:30.273Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t44e5sc7zd1f_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5178\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2043\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master a7b9dcc] pulse: 2026-03-24 142909\n 6 files changed, 284 insertions(+), 107 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 142909.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 142909.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 142713.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 142909 - The CFI Compression Experiment identified that pure CFI thresholds are too aggressive (losing 92.9% recall). The next step is clearly defined: implement and run the hybrid CFIxFreq^0.5 scoring formula to test if it distinguishes constant-format tokens from research trajectory tokens.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"young-lobster","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5178\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2043\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master a7b9dcc] pulse: 2026-03-24 142909\n 6 files changed, 284 insertions(+), 107 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 142909.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 142909.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 142713.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 142909 - The CFI Compression Experiment identified that pure CFI thresholds are too aggressive (losing 92.9% recall). The next step is clearly defined: implement and run the hybrid CFIxFreq^0.5 scoring formula to test if it distinguishes constant-format tokens from research trajectory tokens.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timest